ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實已經唔太睇公式<br />\n一個60kg既人最多食60mg<br />\n我食緊50<br />\n你真係要食得好同斷尾最起碼都20起跳</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次會問下佢可唔可以加量"},{"pid":"b7d4832c2805231cf9bbc487be214f73040e327e","tid":246873,"uid":49290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:50:36.000Z","msg":"開波食20mg 食左兩個月無太大起色<br />\n今次應該轉體重制食 覺得兩個月時間好似哂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}